**TRAVEL JOURNAL**

*1925-1935*

**May 15, 1925**

I set out on the world, a new lawyer. Finally ready to understand what
happened to my family.

**June 22, 1925**

I found the old transfer documents from 1910. Something about them
doesn\'t feel right.

**September 10, 1925**

I\'ve been hired as Scott Thoreson\'s legal assistant. I\'m starting
work next month.

**November 3, 1925**

First day at the Thoreson offices. Strange to be so close to him.

**December 1, 1925**

Scott is kind. Nothing like I expected. The offices are beautiful.

**March 14, 1926**

Attended a dinner party at the estate tonight. The house is enormous. So
many rooms I\'ve never seen.

**September 9, 1927**

Went on a date tonight with a gentleman from the office. He was sweet
but I couldn\'t stop thinking about why I\'m really here. I told him I
had to work late. He didn\'t ask again.

**July 8, 1927**

Scott asked me to organize the library at the house. Spent the whole day
cataloging old files. My hands are dusty but my mind is clear.

**February 3, 1928**

A year and a half now. Time moves differently when you\'re waiting for
something you can\'t quite name.

**October 12, 1929**

The market crashed today. The whole city is panicking. The Theresons
seem untouched by it all.

**May 20, 1931**

Scott promoted me to senior assistant. A raise, more responsibility.
More access to the family documents. He trusts me.

**December 25, 1933**

Spent Christmas at the office. Just me and the empty desks. I found
something today while searching through old papers in the study.
Something I wasn\'t supposed to find. I don\'t know what to do with this
information yet.

**June 1934**

I\'m taking a vacation. Scott approved it without question. Going to
Europe for a few weeks. I need the time away.

**July 1934**

Found what I was looking for in these mountains. Everything is different
now.

**August 1934**

I\'m back. I have what I need. Life continues as it always has.

**March 20, 1935**

Tomorrow is the dinner party. I\'m nervous. Excited. I don\'t know what
will happen.
